Datasource.Parameter: (select * from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% where "natural"='land' order by z_order) as land
(select * from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% where (landuse in ('reservoir', 'water') or "natural" in ('water', 'lake') or waterway in ('riverbank', 'dock', 'basin')) order by z_order) as water
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where (waterway IS NOT NULL and waterway not in ('river', 'stream', 'drain', 'canal', 'dam', 'weir')) order by z_order) as water
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where waterway in ('river', 'stream', 'drain', 'canal', 'dam', 'weir') order by z_order) as water
(select * from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% order by z_order,way_area desc) as leisure

(select way,highway from planet_osm_polygon%zoom% where highway in ('residential','unclassified','pedestrian','service','footway','track', 'living_street') and "area" in ('yes', 'true', '1') order by z_order,way_area desc) as roads

(select way,highway from planet_osm_polygon%zoom% where highway in ('residential','unclassified','pedestrian','service','footway','track', 'living_street') and "area" in ('yes', 'true', '1') order by z_order,way_area desc) as roads
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where tunnel in ('yes', 'true', '1') order by z_order) as roads
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where ((tunnel not in ('yes', 'true', '1') or tunnel is null) and (bridge not in ('yes', 'true', '1') or bridge is null)) order by z_order) as roads
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% order by z_order) as roads
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% order by z_order) as roads
(select * from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% where railway='station' or building='station' order by z_order,way_area desc) as building
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where (waterway='canal' and bridge in ('yes', 'true', '1')) order by z_order) as water
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where bridge in ('yes', 'true') order by z_order) as roads
(select way,highway,railway,name,ref,oneway,area,char_length(ref) as length from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where oneway in ('yes', 'true', '1') ) as roads
(select * from large_cities order by number asc) as large_cities
(select * from %PREFIX%_point%zoom% where (place='city' and (capital not in ('yes') or capital is null))) as cities

(select * from %PREFIX%_point%zoom% where amenity IS NOT NULL or railway is NOT NULL or "natural" is NOT NULL or man_made is NOT NULL or highway is NOT NULL or aeroway is NOT NULL or shop is NOT NULL or tourism is NOT NULL or military is NOT NULL or highway is NOT NULL) as amenity
(select * from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where "power"='line' order by z_order) as power
(select way from %PREFIX%_point%zoom% where power='tower') as power_towers
(select way,highway,landuse,"natural",man_made,waterway,name,ref,char_length(ref) as length from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where waterway IS NULL and leisure IS NULL and landuse IS NULL) as roads
(select way,"addr:housenumber" as name, "addr:interpolation" from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where "addr:interpolation" is not null) as house_line
(select way,"addr:housenumber" as name, char_length("addr:housenumber") as length from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% where "addr:housenumber" is not null) as house_num
(select way,"addr:housenumber" as name, char_length("addr:housenumber") as length from %PREFIX%_point%zoom% where "addr:housenumber" is not null) as house_num
(select * from %PREFIX%_point%zoom% where (place not in ('city') or place is null)) as points

(select way,highway,railway,landuse,"natural",man_made,waterway,tourism,learning,amenity,place,name,ref,oneway,char_length(ref) as length from %PREFIX%_line%zoom% where waterway IS NULL and leisure IS NULL and landuse IS NULL and highway IS NULL and railway IS NULL and "boundary" is null) as roads

(select * from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% where ((leisure not in ('park', 'common', 'golf_course', 'sport_centre', 'stadium', 'track', 'pitch', 'garden') or leisure is null) and (landuse not in ('forest', 'wood', 'residential', 'commercial', 'industrial', 'reservoir', 'water', 'farm') or landuse is null) and ("natural" not in ('wood', 'water', 'lake') or "natural" is null) and (railway !='station' or railway is null) and (aeroway !='terminal' or aeroway is null) and (military != 'danger_area' or military is null) and (amenity not in ('bus_station', 'car_rental', 'school', 'hospital', 'place_of_worship', 'university', 'college') or amenity is null) and (tourism not in ('museum', 'attraction') or tourism is null) and building is null and (highway!='pedestrian' or highway is null) and (waterway!='riverbank' or waterway is null) and (shop!='supermarket' or shop is null)) order by z_order,way_area desc) as leisure

(select * from %PREFIX%_polygon%zoom% where ((leisure in ('park', 'common', 'golf_course', 'sport_centre', 'stadium', 'track', 'pitch', 'garden'))or (landuse in ('forest', 'wood', 'residential', 'commercial', 'industrial', 'reservoir', 'water', 'farm')) or ("natural" in ('wood', 'water', 'lake')) or railway='station' or building is not null or aeroway='terminal' or military='danger_area' or amenity in ('bus_station', 'car_rental', 'university', 'college', 'school', 'place_of_worship', 'hospital') or tourism in ('museum', 'attraction') or highway='pedestrian' or waterway='riverbank' or shop='supermarket') order by z_order,way_area desc) as leisure
